comments:
Created 1.4.1903 out of the parishes of Llandybie and Bettws. 
    See also Table 2, note (b).
Abolished 1.4.1935 and added to the parish of Llanegwad.

Created 1.4.1912 out of the parishes of Bettws and Llandilo Rural. 
    See also Table 2, note (b).

That part which until 1.4.1935 formed parts of the parishes of 
    Llanegwad and Llangathen. See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of Llandilo Urban 
    and Llandilo Rural.

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Llandilofawr. 
    See also Table 2, note (b).

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Llandilofawr in Llandilo 
    Urban District. See also Table 2, note (b).
Abolished 1.4.1935 and added to the parish of Llangathen.
